"bar-9c1669ce60c3f4f5eb43df874d7314483fb3f8a6-9c1669ce60c3f4f5eb43df874d7314483fb3f8a6`."

#. type: delimited block = 6
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/makefiles/_index.adoc:1954
